et_high_price":155.0,"target_low_price":152.0,"target_mean_price":153.5,"recommendation":"strong_buy","num_analyst_opinions":2,"all_time_high":279.4,"all_time_low":99.48,"long_business_summary":"Rolex Rings Limited manufactures and sell of forged and machined bearing rings, and automotive components in India and internationally. It offers transmission components, such as gear blanks, ring gears, sun and pinion, shafts, and lock nuts; and chasis components comprising wheel hubs, gen2 and gen3 bearing components, output shafts, and CVJ components. The company also provides bearing rings, such as TRB, CRB, SRB, SPB, DGBB, angular contact, and double row bearings. Its products are used in industrial, railways, off highway, earth moving, windmill, textile, electrical, defense, power, aerospace, marine, and oil and natural gas industries, as well as for two, three, and four wheelers. Rolex Rings Limited was founded in 1977 and is based in Rajkot, India."}}